{"tid":738209,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《銀河守衛隊》演員加盟DC《沙讚》","createTime":"2018-07-11T10:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T11:14:36.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6467f0c9a09b3b1625b98524876c30fe0c9692","tid":738209,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"《銀河守衛隊》男星Djimon Hounsou將出演 《沙贊》中的巫師一角。<br />\n<br />\n以超級英雄迷來說，對於這位演員的認識，應該是在漫威電影《銀河守衛隊》飾演不認識星爵並說出 WHO 的傭兵 Korath the Pursuer，而同樣的角色也會出現在設定在 90 年代的驚奇隊長個人電影裡面。<br />\n<br />\n此前早的2005年，他曾出演根據DC漫畫 《康斯坦丁》改編的奇幻恐怖片《地獄神探》（奇洛李維斯主演）中的午夜老爹一角，可謂多次橫跨DC和漫威的男演員了。<br />\n<br />\n首任巫師沙讚是永恆議會的創立者，他用3000年的時間對抗世間邪惡，他最終選擇了比利&middot;巴特森作為人類的守護者，將所羅門、海格力斯、阿特拉斯、宙斯、阿基里斯、墨丘利的能力授予了年輕的比利&middot;巴特森，也就是後來的超級英雄沙讚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2014/04/11/article-2602074-1D0261D300000578-410_634x341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2014%2F04%2F11%2Farticle-2602074-1D0261D300000578-410_634x341.jpg&h=edb00026&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c00629a417659ff68828f89545966200a4d2c96d","tid":738209,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"dc 又贏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950092a4f90cac10b6a4f8a818c0d0f68ce0220c","tid":738209,"uid":155818,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T10:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1tj37QX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1tj37QX.gif&h=a5695063&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b68470c1a8176b4adc077ca34a27d4cef04c351","tid":738209,"uid":29982,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"